A:L^2[-\pi,\pi]\rightarrow L^2[-\pi,\pi]
Af(x)=\int_{-\pi}^{\pi} \cos^2{\left(\frac{x-t}{2}\right)}f(t) \,dt.
\|A\|\leq 2\pi
f = \cos(nx)
(Af)(x) = \int_{-\pi}^\pi\cos^2\left(\frac{x-t}{2}\right)\cos(nt)\,dt = \begin{cases}\frac{1}{2}\pi\cos(x) & n = 1.\\ 0 & n>1.\end{cases}
f \equiv 1
(Af)(x) = \int_{-\pi}^\pi \cos^2\left(\frac{x-t}{2}\right)\,dt \equiv \pi.
A
\|A\| = \pi
\|Af\| = \pi\|f\|
